<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="title">每日记录</view>
    <view class="subtitle">Daily todo、健康和学习打卡的小程序骨架。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">首页</view>
    <view class="muted">这里后续展示今天的记录概览和快速入口。</view>
    <view class="card-list">
      <view class="placeholder-card" wx:for="{{cards}}" wx:key="title">
        <view class="card-title">{{item.title}}</view>
        <view class="card-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
